						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">lidnariq wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Slow down everything by 0.16%. Frame rate would become exactly 60 Hz; CPU now runs at 1.78683MHz; PPU pixel clock becomes 5.36049MHz, &amp;c.</div><br /><br />You could do: 60.098814/60 = 1,0016469<br /><br />and then do 44100 * 1,0016469 = 44173 for sample rate. (still might have rounding errors)</div>

